quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  45,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  45,1,h m
  45,2,iss kitaab ka nuzool Allah ki taraf se hai jo zabardast aur hakeem hai
  45,3,haqeeqat yeh hai ke asmano aur zameen mein be shumaar nishanain hain imaan laane walon ke liye
  45,4,"aur tumhari apni paidaiesh mein, aur unn hewanat mein jin ko Allah ( zameen mein ) phela raha hai, barri nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo yaqeen laane walay hain"
  45,5,"aur shab o roz ke farq o ikhtilaaf mein, aur uss rizaq mein jisay Allah aasman se nazil farmata hai phir is ke zareya se murda zameen ko jِla uthata hai, aur hawaon ki gardish mein bohat nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain"
  45,6,yeh Allah ki nishanain hain jinhein hum tumahray samnay theek theek bayan kar rahay hain ab aakhir Allah aur is ki ayaat ke baad aur kon si baat hai jis par yeh log imaan layein ge
  45,7,tabahi hai har uss jhutay bad aamaal shakhs ke liye
  45,8,"jis ke samnay Allah ki ayaat parhi jati hain, aur woh unn ko santa hai, phir poooray istakbar (takabbur) ke sath apne kufar par iss terhan ura rehta hai ke goya is ne unn ko suna hi nahi aisay shakhs ko dard naak azaab ka Musda suna do"
  45,9,hamari ayaat mein se koi baat jab is ke ilm mein aati hai to woh unn ka mazaq bana laita hai aisay sab logon ke liye zillat ka azaab hai
  45,10,"unn ke agay jahannum hai jo kuch bhi unhon ne duniya mein kamaya hai is mein se koi cheez unn ke kisi kaam nah aeye gi, nah unn ke woh sarparast hi unn ke liye kuch kar saken ge jinhein Allah ko chore kar unhon ne apna walii bana rakha hai unn ke liye bara azaab hai"
  45,11,"yeh quran sara sar hadaayat hai, aur unn logon ke liye bulaa ka dard naak azaab hai jinhon ne apne rab ki ayaat ko maan-ne se inkaar kya"
  45,12,woh Allah hi to hai jis ne tumahray liye samandar ko maskhar kya taakay is ke hukum se kashtiyan uss mein chalein aur tum is ka fazl talaash karo aur shukar guzaar ho
  45,13,"is ne zameen aur asmano ki saari hi cheezon ko tumahray liye maskhar kar diya, sab kuch apne paas se iss mein barri nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar karne walay hain"
  45,14,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, imaan laane walon se keh do ke jo log Allah ki taraf se buray din anay ka koi andesha nahi rakhtay, unn ki harkato par dar guzar se kaam len taakay Allah khud aik giroh ko is ki kamaai ka badla day"
  45,15,"jo koi naik amal kere ga apne hi liye kere ga, aur jo buraiee kere ga woh aap hi is ka khmyazh bhugtey ga phir jana to sab ko apne rab hi ki taraf hai"
  45,16,"iss se pehlay bani Israel ko hum ne kitaab aur hukum aur nabuwat ataa ki thi unn ko hum ne umdah samaan zeist se nawaza, duniya bhar ke logon par inhen fazeelat ataa ki"
  45,17,aur deen ke maamla mein unhen wazeh Hadayat day den phir jo ikhtilaaf unn ke darmain ro numa howa woh ( na waqfiyat ki wajah se nahi balkay ) ilm aa jaane ke baad howa aur is bana par howa ke woh aapas mein aik dosray par zayad-ti karna chahtay thay Allah qayamat ke roz unn mamlaat ka faisla farma day ga jin mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain
  45,18,"is ke baad ab ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tum ko deen ke maamla mein aik saaf shahrah ( Shariat ) par qaim kya hai lehaza tum isi par chalo aur unn logon ki khwahisaat ka itebaa nah karo jo ilm nahi rakhtay"
  45,19,"Allah ke muqablay mein woh tumahray kuch bhi kaam nahi aa satke zalim log aik dosray ke saathi hain, aur Muttaqiyun ka saathi Allah hai"
  45,20,yeh baseerat ki roshniyan hain sab logon ke liye aur hadaayat aur rehmat unn logon ke liye jo yaqeen layein
  45,21,kya woh log jinhon ne buraiyon ka irtikaab kya hai yeh samjhay baithy hain ke hum unhen aur imaan laane walon aur naik amal karne walon ko aik jaissa kar den ge ke un ka jeena aur marna yaksaa ho jaye? bohat buray hukum hain jo yeh log lagatay hain
  45,22,Allah ne to asmano aur zameen ko brhq peda kya hai aur is liye kya hai ke har mutnaqas ko uss ki kamaai ka badla diya jaye logon par zulm hargiz nah kya jaye ga
  45,23,phir kya tum ne kabhi uss shakhs ke haal par bhi ghhor kya jis ne apni khwahish nafs ko apna khuda bana liya aur Allah ne ilm ke bawajood ussay gumraahi mein pheink diya aur uss ke dil aur kaanon par mohar laga di aur uss ki aankhon par parda daal diya? Allah ke baad ab aur kon hai jo ussay hadaayat day? kya tum log koi sabaq nahi letay ?
  45,24,"yeh log kehte hain ke"" zindagi bas yahi hamari duniya ki zindagi hai, yahin hamara marna aur jeena hai aur gardish ayyaam ke siwa koi cheez nahi jo hamein halaak karti ho"" Dur haqeeqat iss maamla mein inn ke paas koi ilm nahi hai yeh mehez gumaan ki bana par yeh baatein karte hain"
  45,25,aur jab hamari wazeh ayaat inhen sunai jati hain to inn ke paas koi Hujjat is ke siwa nahi hoti ke utha lao hamaray baap dada ko agar tum sachey ho
  45,26,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho Allah hi tumhe zindagi bkhshta hai, phir wohi tumhe mout deta hai, phir wohi tum ko uss qayamat ke din jama kere ga jis ke anay mein koi shak nahi, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  45,27,"zameen aur asmano ki badshahi Allah hi ki hai, aur jis roz qayamat ki gharri aa khari ho gi uss din baatil parast khasaray mein par jayen ge"
  45,28,"uss waqt tum har giroh ko ghutnon ke bil gira dekho ge har giroh ko puraka jaye ga ke aeye aur apna nama aamaal dekhe unn se kaha jaye ga :"" aaj tum logon ko unn aamaal ka badla diya jaye ga jo tum karte rahay thay"
  45,29,"yeh hamara tayyar karaya howa aamaal nama hai jo tumahray oopar theek theek shahadat day raha hai, jo kuch bhi tum karte thay ussay hum lkhwate ja rahay thay """
  45,30,phir jo log imaan laaye thay aur naik amal karte rahay thay inhen un ka rab apni rehmat mein daakhil kere ga aur yahi Sarih kamyabi hai
  45,31,"aur jin logon ne kufar kya tha unn se kaha jaye ga"" kya meri ayaat tum ko nahi sunai jati theen? magar tum ne taqqabur kya aur mujrim ban kar rahay"
  45,32,"aur jab kaha jata tha ke Allah ka wada brhq hai aur qayamat ke anay mein koi shak nahi, to tum kehte thay ke hum nahi jantay qayamat kya hoti hai, hum to bas aik gumaan sa rakhtay hain, yaqeen hum ko nahi hai """
  45,33,uss waqt unn par un ke aamaal ki buraiyan khil jayen gi aur woh usi cheez ke phair mein aa jayen ge jis ka woh mazaq uraya karte thay
  45,34,"aur un se keh diya jaye ga ke"" aaj hum bhi usi terhan tumhe bhulae dete hain jis terhan tum iss din ki mulaqaat ko bhool gay thay tumhara thikana ab dozakh hai aur koi tumhari madad karne wala nahi hai"
  45,35,"yeh tumhara injaam is liye howa hai ke tum ne Allah ki ayaat ka mazaq bana liya tha aur tumhe duniya ki zindagi ne dhokay mein daal diya tha lehaza aaj nah yeh log dozakh se nikalay jayen ge aur nah un se kaha jaye ga ke maffi maang kar apne rab ko raazi karo """
  45,36,pas tareef Allah hi ke liye hai jo zameen aur asmano ka maalik aur saaray Jahan walon ka parvar-digaar hai
  45,37,zameen aur asmano mein barayi usi ke liye hai aur wohi zabardast aur Dana hai
